&lt;p&gt;Octagon Medical Practice is a merger of practices in the Peterborough area, and as such is owned and run by the partners from those practices. We are contracted by the NHS to provide Primary Care Services through our various locations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nene Valley Surgery in Peterborough are looking for a Referrals Administrator to work 30 hours per week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To be succcessful in this role, you will need good IT/database skills, excellent customer service skills, the ability to communicate clearly and confidently, be orgnaised, efficient and a strong team-player. You will need to be able to work under pressure, follow instructions and complete tasks as scheduled. This is a great opportunity for anyone looking to expand their customer service and administrative skills within a busy team environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you believe you have the right skills for this post, then Octagon would love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
